      public void setEnforceOneToOneRelationships(boolean enforceOneToOneRelationships)
      When set to true, it will enforce one-to-one relationships for SBOL graphs that are generated by other tools. For performance reasons, if the graphs are created by libSBOLj, then this property can be set to false.
